  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927050/extras/9b71c6b3fcc1e1dff2f4229774e6a77d.poster.avif?t=1766978507\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927050/extras/9b71c6b3fcc1e1dff2f4229774e6a77d.webm?t=1766978507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927050/extras/9b71c6b3fcc1e1dff2f4229774e6a77d.mp4?t=1766978507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Rotate Your Way Out</strong></h2></h2></h2>GlassBox is a unique 3D puzzle game that will challenge your spatial visualisation, logic, accuracy and speed. Every level is a glass box maze you can rotate and your goal is to get a ball out of it, you can choose your ball, but you only control the box.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Be Patient, Be Smart, then Be Fast</strong></h2>Take your time to understand the logic of a level, from a simple to a complex box. Once you get it, try and finish as fast as possible. Every level has 3 times to beat - bronze, silver and gold. Beat the best time and get a unique reward in coins with a special audio feedback.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Find the Right One </strong></h2>Unlock all the balls with coins or in levels. Every ball has a different shape, grip, weight and size. Use Their variation to help you finish every level with the best time, which ball for which level? try to figuring it out!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927050/extras/d917d20538c49d4ee9fbe614d782ea23.poster.avif?t=1766978507\" width=100 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927050/extras/d917d20538c49d4ee9fbe614d782ea23.webm?t=1766978507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927050/extras/d917d20538c49d4ee9fbe614d782ea23.mp4?t=1766978507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927050/extras/27e601b04717af96f1ea097ab64ca5a8.poster.avif?t=1766978507\" width=100 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927050/extras/27e601b04717af96f1ea097ab64ca5a8.webm?t=1766978507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927050/extras/27e601b04717af96f1ea097ab64ca5a8.mp4?t=1766978507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927050/extras/d055b110067fad1b9fe42bf3c2a4ecf8.poster.avif?t=1766978507\" width=100 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927050/extras/d055b110067fad1b9fe42bf3c2a4ecf8.webm?t=1766978507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927050/extras/d055b110067fad1b9fe42bf3c2a4ecf8.mp4?t=1766978507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927050/extras/f114457b087ca4eab8acc1bf5916acf4.poster.avif?t=1766978507\" width=100 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927050/extras/f114457b087ca4eab8acc1bf5916acf4.webm?t=1766978507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927050/extras/f114457b087ca4eab8acc1bf5916acf4.mp4?t=1766978507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927050/extras/8dec744393a471db65e4fe76f8c90938.poster.avif?t=1766978507\" width=100 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927050/extras/8dec744393a471db65e4fe76f8c90938.webm?t=1766978507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927050/extras/8dec744393a471db65e4fe76f8c90938.mp4?t=1766978507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927050/extras/cd1feffe191459eb77170760458922af.poster.avif?t=1766978507\" width=100 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927050/extras/cd1feffe191459eb77170760458922af.webm?t=1766978507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927050/extras/cd1feffe191459eb77170760458922af.mp4?t=1766978507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927050/extras/9b71c6b3fcc1e1dff2f4229774e6a77d.poster.avif?t=1766978507\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927050/extras/9b71c6b3fcc1e1dff2f4229774e6a77d.webm?t=1766978507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927050/extras/9b71c6b3fcc1e1dff2f4229774e6a77d.mp4?t=1766978507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Rotate Your Way Out</strong></h2></h2></h2>GlassBox is a unique 3D puzzle game that will challenge your spatial visualisation, logic, accuracy and speed. Every level is a glass box maze you can rotate and your goal is to get a ball out of it, you can choose your ball, but you only control the box.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Be Patient, Be Smart, then Be Fast</strong></h2>Take your time to understand the logic of a level, from a simple to a complex box. Once you get it, try and finish as fast as possible. Every level has 3 times to beat - bronze, silver and gold. Beat the best time and get a unique reward in coins with a special audio feedback.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Find the Right One </strong></h2>Unlock all the balls with coins or in levels. Every ball has a different shape, grip, weight and size. Use Their variation to help you finish every level with the best time, which ball for which level? try to figuring it out!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927050/extras/d917d20538c49d4ee9fbe614d782ea23.poster.avif?t=1766978507\" width=100 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/a